headline: Prediction: This Hot Artificial Intelligence (AI) Semiconductor Stock Will Skyrocket After June 25
summary: Micron Technology stock has been in red-hot form on the stock market over the past couple of months, and its upcoming quarterly report on June 25 could give it another boost.  Micron is on track to deliver outstanding growth in its revenue and earnings, driven by the terrific demand for the company's high-bandwidth memory chips.  Micron Technology (NASDAQ: MU) stock has made a sharp move higher over the past couple of months -- gaining an impressive 37% as of this writing -- driven by the broader recovery in technology stocks.
